text.section:
This subtitle does not apply to:
A close corporation as defined in § 4-101(b) of this article;
A corporation having fewer than 100 beneficial owners of its stock;
A corporation registered under the Investment Company Act of 1940 as an open end investment company; or
A corporation registered under the Investment Company Act of 1940 as a closed end investment company unless its board of directors adopts a resolution to be subject to this subtitle on or after June 1, 2000, provided that the resolution shall not be effective with respect to any person who has become a holder of control shares before the time that the resolution is adopted.
